      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"اَلصَّمْتُ كَنْزٌ وَافِرٌ وَ زَيْنُ اَلْحَلِيمِ وَ سِتْرُ اَلْجَاهِلِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5843 - Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as), said:\n\"Silence is a vast treasure, the adornment of the wise, and a covering for the ignorant.\""
        ]
